version_description: These chords definitely work with the song and can be played along to, though it doesn't sound exactly like the original. The original has a lot more open strings tuned differently, so this is as close as I could get with standard tuning. Still works great and is a lot of fun to play though.
For just a "chords" tab, this here "chords" tab is incredibally accurate and even follows the actual key changes in the song - this will make you so happy to learn. You don't even know.
